<P>
   (UNDATED) _ Could this week mark the great schism that
eventually tears apart OPEC? Only time will tell. But what is clear
is that Saudi Arabia has decided to lift the veil of pretense and
admit that the cartel is mere window-dressing for its political and
economic agenda, a convenient fiction to be tolerated in good times
but disregarded in crisis. &QL;
