<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-07 13:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5458 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-BUGGED-EMBASSY-BOS &LR;      07-07 0753
