<P>
   COXNET NASCAR PAGE
</P>
<P>
   Following is a budget for this week's Inside NASCAR page. The
page will be available Thursday before 3 p.m. EDT. For questions,
call CoxNet at (404) 526-5456.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET INSIDE NASCAR 0707: JARRETT QUIETLY GETTING IT DONE _ As
Dale Jarrett's No. 88 Ford team heads toward the midway part of the
season, the Winston Cup champ is in prime position to repeat. Mired
in eighth place after seven races, Jarrett quietly has risen to
third. But the fact that he hasn't dominated this season has some
fans wondering what is wrong. (Levine, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
