<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-07 17:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5917 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-TEN-WIMBLEDON-WOMEN-B     07-07 0954
