<P>
   Editors at publications outside the United States may find the
following stories from the New York Times News Service that are
scheduled for release on  &UR; SUNDAY, &LR;  July 9, of particular interest.
We plan to move these stories by 2 p.m. EDT on Saturday, July 8.
