<HEADLINE>
NEW POTTER BOOK IS BEST OF THE BUNCH 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  (Editors: ``Galleons'' in 10th graf is CQ.) 
 
By JANE P. MARSHALL 
c.2000 Houston Chronicle 
