   &QR;  The Norton Museum of Art in West Palm Beach, Fla.:
</P>
<P>
   www.norton.org
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  The High Museum of Art:
</P>
<P>
   www.high.org
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  The Cheekwood Art Museum in Nashville:
</P>
<P>
   www.cheekwood.org
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  The Tampa Museum of Art:
</P>
<P>
   www.tampamuseum.com
</P>
