Rodney Orr, 1994, Daytona, Fla. &QL; 
Neil Bonnett, 1994, Daytona, Fla. &QL; 
Clifford Allison, 1992, Brooklyn, Mich. &QL; 
J.D. McDuffie, 1991, Watkins Glen, N.Y. &QL; 
Grant Adcox, 1989, Hampton, Ga. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-07-07-00 2034EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
