about American officials' views as to the seriousness of missile
threats posed by countries including North Korea, Iran and Iraq
misstated the service background of Larry D. Welch, who heads an
independent panel reviewing the Pentagon's missile defense plans.
He is a retired general in the Air Force, not the Army.  &QL;
