<HEADLINE>
GRANDSON OF DODGERS STAR IS CHARGED IN FRIEND'S ACCIDENTAL DEATH 
</HEADLINE>
   (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in category ``s'')  
 By ALAN FEUER   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
